{"tid":917382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我後知後覺，但我終於醒..離開個賤男","createTime":"2018-11-26T11:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T11:49:01.000Z","uid":224051,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7e75d68b61cba62eb972e56c0bb0ece776144dbf","tid":917382,"uid":224051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:15:47.000Z","msg":"一開始識呢個人，<span style=\"color: red;\">我唔知佢已經有個兩，三年嘅女朋友.</span>佢亦都同我講佢冇女朋友.<br />\n而且大家一直做嘅嘢已經超越朋友關係.到我開口暗示話想拍拖 佢都會話單身幾好點好咁.<br />\n<br />\n到之後佢個朋友先話我知 佢有女朋友..個男仔就同我講話唔想大家冇朋友做..如事者，我就繼續同佢咁嘅關係..<br />\n我發現一直以尼除左我，佢女朋友，原來仲有其他人..<br />\n到我問佢 佢永遠只會講大話 到我有圖有證據 佢先至會肯認..<br />\n<br />\n我知係我自己攞尼賤 明知人地有女朋友仲中個頭埋去 ..明知佢係啲咁嘅人 都繼續中意佢 我就係咁犯賤..<br />\n我同個男仔講過好多次 但佢都只係逃避 唔肯俾答案我<br />\n<br />\n無可否認我好唔甘心，試問有幾多人會唔想做正印 想做小三。同我唔想再便宜左個男仔 點解佢一直都可以左擁右抱<br />\n<br />\n所以我最後決定話俾佢女朋友知.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/190735_427face7891ef001edae94e3be5971f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F190735_427face7891ef001edae94e3be5971f5.png&h=fe7710ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/190902_2441aa876c87c77e0dd7bdef3812fbe9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F190902_2441aa876c87c77e0dd7bdef3812fbe9.png&h=78446790&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/191003_ce6a2cb94fb473a6ae890519aeec07fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F191003_ce6a2cb94fb473a6ae890519aeec07fb.png&h=3fe2b00f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/191043_76c4dc6beda095762afc2c3e665c14f3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F191043_76c4dc6beda095762afc2c3e665c14f3.png&h=43f2d1a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/191151_e378c171668ad84ddc59e4a3ba9a0a2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F191151_e378c171668ad84ddc59e4a3ba9a0a2b.png&h=2847b975&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/191429_a3dc7b668347f0663bf6572bdd537f4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F191429_a3dc7b668347f0663bf6572bdd537f4d.png&h=61d01339&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/26/191520_c1f38178d64866b13e11103917f5b079.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F26%2F191520_c1f38178d64866b13e11103917f5b079.png&h=06e87ecc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72c252275769e3d8043ee9c2abe8c8a384c41b56","tid":917382,"uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:17:22.000Z","msg":"WFC"},{"pid":"3733a598714af84b5db3d43b3641132226821f96","tid":917382,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"關我鳩事咩"},{"pid":"5c37407a24a2383e54a35844f574fcfeb599f562","tid":917382,"uid":42487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:33:08.000Z","msg":"做開雞，平d益巴打啦"},{"pid":"cf14095d1d87f2504046f8b8385921b83296adf4","tid":917382,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:35:42.000Z","msg":"男仔叫柒頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1f0fb2284a27d0621c06ea12118ed9d6d01618","tid":917382,"uid":69694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"尼你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a312e1eafb5e170e75eb3a58c82e1ad0083199ee","tid":917382,"uid":24559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-